sequenceDiagram
  participant B as Master BDMA/IPC
  participant TOP as TOP regs
  participant SF as User sf
  participant CMD as User cmd_entry
  participant IB as Interaction Buffer
  participant CPE as CPE regs

  B->>TOP: STOP_HCQDID = BIT(hcqd)
  TOP-->>SF: IRQ_STOP_REQ / CPE_HCQD_STOPPED bitmap
  SF->>SF: stop_bitmask |= hcqd_bitmap
  CMD->>CMD: active includes stop_bitmask
  CMD->>SF: sf_handle_stop(hcqd)
  SF->>IB: ib_read_packet + ib_drop_packet for resident packets
  SF->>CPE: set CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED bit
  B->>TOP: poll HCQD_STATUS stop complete
  B->>CPE: poll CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED
  B->>TOP: RELEASE_HCQDID set/clear
  B->>CPE: clear CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED
  B->>TOP: STOP_HCQDID = 0
